{"tid":1448361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無限期塞地鐵引發持續大罷工的時候到了","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:56:24.000Z","uid":269717,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc47142d246c4ccd205630d9e942084fe2806369","tid":1448361,"uid":269717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"811發生的事，是現今文明城市不敢想象的。地鐵站內近距離掃射市民，引發踩踏。北角警黑勾結，無法無天。隨意向街坊發射催淚彈胡椒噴霧。這樣的香港，不如焦土後重生。<br />\n<br />\n以後所有無限期塞地鐵，塞隧道，大罷工不要覺得奇怪。若現在誰要返工，抵做一世奴隸。<br />\n<br />\n和理非的極限是罷工。勇武派會給大家創造無限條件持續大罷工。721 811徹底改變香港，也會改變世界和共產黨的壽命期限<br />\n<br />\n無限期塞地鐵，塞隧道罷工時候到了"},{"pid":"c6b8a6028e0c10a511de14820c88bb5397346e7c","tid":1448361,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"有咩高效率嘅塞地鐵方法？"},{"pid":"f4b6a2f3a6602ceb9454f65ececfe78e2bd307b0","tid":1448361,"uid":269717,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8a6028e0c10a511de14820c88bb5397346e7c","tid":1448361,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"有咩高效率嘅塞地鐵方法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:35:03.000Z","msg":"只需要幾百人，分幾個關鍵站就能達到效果。成本低，效率高。另外需要文宣mtr站內無限loop掃射是您視頻，和女子眼球爆的視頻，讓政府無法翻身"},{"pid":"da92f2822c36dc32a61f4fcccbb10b026f9f959b","tid":1448361,"uid":244691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"推 攬抄&gt;送終"},{"pid":"a949737d8fed4d66092be1b56f95af6a11ade75c","tid":1448361,"uid":258088,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:40:01.000Z","msg":"一人一Post狂洗連登 [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=7f50c605\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=a46b2b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"5573e82d1fef19afab5e5dceee6503f0e7a75f39","tid":1448361,"uid":140785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"塞左鐵點入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6f1e7048f069c3b9cb2d6f79233599e917671d","tid":1448361,"uid":269717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qm9E3Qi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQm9E3Qi.png&h=dc2e42ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6fa95740c80ddadce0c18d935e0643d091bc2dda","tid":1448361,"uid":271413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c6b8a6028e0c10a511de14820c88bb5397346e7c","tid":1448361,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"有咩高效率嘅塞地鐵方法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:13.000Z","msg":"只要狗鐵內部有人搞亂訊號系統就得，但冇人咁做"},{"pid":"209490eb8895a4b33441e5ab4d2649207c1e94b3","tid":1448361,"uid":69221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5573e82d1fef19afab5e5dceee6503f0e7a75f39","tid":1448361,"uid":140785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"塞左鐵點入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:58.000Z","msg":"巴士，的士"},{"pid":"22d3854f5655aa5d0e1431c711ad31cca37baa61","tid":1448361,"uid":140785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2094